high_descs: Move over to the desk in front of the clock on the left.
Pick up the clock on the left.
Bring the clock over to the desk next to the couch.
Turn on the light on the desk.
Turn around, head towards the desk on the right, and turn left to face the desk.
Pick up the alarm clock closest to the chair.
Turn around and head towards the green lamp on the desk.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a alarm clock by the light of a green lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and go back to the large desk.
Pick up the clock from the left side of the desk.
Carry the clock and turn to the left, then the left again to locate another desk.
Hold the clock and turn on the lamp on the left side of the desk.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a clock and turn on the lamp.

high_descs: Turn around, move forward, turn left to face the table with two clocks.
Pick up the clock on the front edge of the table.
Turn to your left, take a step, turn left again, and move until you face a table with a lamp and a cell phone
Turn on the lamp
anns.task_desc: Pick up a clock and turn on a lamp

high_descs: turn to the right twice and go to the desk chair and turn to the left and step to the desk
pick up the clock from the desk
turn to the left and take a few steps and turn to the left and go to the desk
turn on the lamp on the desk
anns.task_desc: Examine a clock by the light of a desk lamp

high_descs: turn right, turn right,walk to desk, turn left, pick up clock,turn left, walk to table
pick up clock from desk, turn left, walk to table, turn left
